comments.body: I'm not sure I see the error. What error do you get?
Only these logs gets printed in console.after that it only gets failed and does not return any log in console.But this scenario does not happen every time.

Hello,

I have tested this issue in updated environment. This is not a bug  for  latest Appcelerator version.  Not sure if this is still an issue for you.It doesn't appear to be based on our latest tests.I recommend you upgrade studio to the latest build and let us know if you get the error again. Please let us  know how I can help further.
